      "filename": "punch_high_000.png through punch_high_009.png",
      "source_sheet": "chatgpt_punch_high_board_v1",
      "note": "10-frame high punch (jab to the face) generated by ChatGPT from a 5x2 green-screen reference board (referencing the pack's own kick_high for the target head-height hit line), replacing a prior 3-frame punch_high that incorrectly landed at the same chest height as punch_mid. Chroma-keyed and re-composited onto the standard 256x256 canvas using a single fixed scale factor (derived from the standing guard frame, punch_high_000) applied to every frame; feet stay at anchor y=214, centered at x=128.",
